      "created_at": "2021-02-17T17:53:31.760Z",
      "updated_at": "2021-02-17T17:53:31.760Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yeah I do get it with all speeds, some speeds just exaggerate the effect more than others.</p>\n<p>Here is a pic of the patch:<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/6/6737298b198b9d672fdccf7697bba45e1560694d.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/eJ5mzzEq2b6loIguyjlkgyI5Ohf.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"IMG_1401\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/6/6737298b198b9d672fdccf7697bba45e1560694d.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_1401\" data-base62-sha1=\"eJ5mzzEq2b6loIguyjlkgyI5Ohf\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_1401</span><span class=\"informations\">4032\u00d73024 2.8 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/5/5765b1302def6b7a80960aaf44b3f4149be65732.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/ct9pGI9RAqlDggL1FiKFyQEqweu.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"IMG_1400\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/5/5765b1302def6b7a80960aaf44b3f4149be65732.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_1400\" data-base62-sha1=\"ct9pGI9RAqlDggL1FiKFyQEqweu\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_1400</span><span class=\"informations\">3838\u00d72878 3.12 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></